        "TileImage": "$($repository 040fa3cc-be7c-4428-a3b7-3f5828bd2786).Image",
        "Description": "Good evening 47, and welcome to Colorado, USA. Today we have a very difficult and different mission. I have received that some ex-IGAO employees have decided to try again, and are building new forces and kidnapping one of the ICA leaders in a final bastion of IGAO. You must eliminate five targets, who are currently the leaders of the base. In addition to them, try to eliminate as many IGAO soldiers as possible, if not the entire base. Good hunting 47.",
